text:
Safe, clean, comfortable, and convenient... Can't ask for much more! Roman greeted me and got me settled and left me to do my thing, but remained readily available via text. 

Approximately 5-10 minutes and $5 to take an uber into town.; 15 minutes and $15 to the airport.

Check out Kebabalicious on E. 7th or "El Sol y la Luna" downtown on 6th... My two fav eats from my stay!
title: Private Studio in Modern Crash Pad
